Draws a figure with one node per modality of \code{fact} (2 to 4 supported),
positioned on a regular polygon. Each node is a pie chart showing the
taxonomic composition at rank \code{pie_taxrank}. Between each pair of nodes,
one curved link per metric is drawn; linewidth is rescaled within each
metric to \code{linewidth_range}. A legend below the figure gives each metric's
min / mean / max over all pairs.
}
\details{
